{"tid":2176827,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［廣傳］港共拒絕HKFP入境 上咗路透中國twitter","createTime":"2020-08-27T10:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T14:14:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f05db62cb3d9095ba6a1584f09468b5d7af1b37c","tid":2176827,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/reuterschina/status/1298924403556618240?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Freuterschina%2Fstatus%2F1298924403556618240%3Fs%3D21&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=666745fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Freuterschina%2Fstatus%2F1298924403556618240%3Fs%3D21&h=79029eb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/reuterschina/status/1298924403556618240?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"3e5305a9cdfce89932e3ba160b5b1dc3bbaa4d84","tid":2176827,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:16:57.000Z","msg":"有傳入境處已成立新的國安部門處理外媒記者簽證申請，但處方至今未有回應事件。英文網媒Hong Kong Free Press（HKFP）發聲明，指該報一名新任編緝經過六個月等候，本周二（25日）突遭入境處在沒有提供解說情況下拒絕其簽證申請，認為情況進一步令香港在《國安法》下的商業社會、新聞自由更令人擔憂，HKFP促請政府提供拒絕的理由，並稱考慮提出司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\nHKFP在新聞稿中指，周二收到入境處電郵通知員工簽證被拒，但未有解釋拒絕申請的原因，僅表示香港有開放政策處理僱員海外專業人士。<br />\n<br />\nHKFP總編緝Tom Grundy指出，不少媒體正遭遇人員簽證申請延誤的問題，但HKFP為本地媒體，該名新任編緝是來自愛爾蘭的記者，認為對方簽證申請被拒與中美貿易戰無關，直言情況反映出一種新模式，令他們在新《國安法》下，因其公正且基於事實的報道受針對。<br />\n<br />\nTom Grundy續指，其他行業都可能會面對《國安法》下形成的官僚、冗長的手續，簽證被視為國安法下的一種功能，企業或將不再視香港為合適的區域基地。<br />\n<br />\n保護記者委員會亞洲項目協調員Steven Butler在聲明中表示，拒絕向本地媒體人員發出簽證，違反香港特區政府反覆強調新聞自由的最基本承諾，嚴重破壞香港的國際城及金融中心地位，而新聞工作者自由地工作是當中要訣。無國界記者組織東亞辦事處主任C&eacute;dric Alviani亦於聲明表示，特區政府必須撤回這個有違《基本法》中保障的新聞自由的決定，認為今次事件是香港實施國安法，准許內地直接介入香港事務後，另一個反映香港新聞自由衰退的訊號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/5AACWK6TCNDLLANSTDGODTQUJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2F5AACWK6TCNDLLANSTDGODTQUJA%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=d3c7afaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2F5AACWK6TCNDLLANSTDGODTQUJA%2F&h=f21b8b5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/5AACWK6TCNDLLANSTDGODTQUJA/</a>"},{"pid":"39dbe352857179285faa36a94ab3698c7cff0485","tid":2176827,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6865c818fa41754429a57d3b07f88e9b994d68b9","tid":2176827,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:19:43.000Z","msg":"BINC<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/05/carrie-lam-security-laws-affect-hong-kong-freedoms-200526032556555.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F05%2Fcarrie-lam-security-laws-affect-hong-kong-freedoms-200526032556555.html&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=fd8d4ea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/05/carrie-lam-security-laws-affect-hong-kong-freedoms-200526032556555.html</a>"},{"pid":"568b2c5c182b4333133d0010efb0acd0f07550a9","tid":2176827,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe9d7f5c9eadb1eb3ff61febbfa2e37db931051","tid":2176827,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b59b8fa6aba146d07ad609bcba9e7102c0a9ea82","tid":2176827,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"無記者就無報道無live，可以為所欲為"},{"pid":"f2d3d68160f2f2704c4